These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, entrepreneur, mechanic, paramedic, photographer, social-worker, videographer
There 7 different types of food: garlic, strawberry, apple, papaya, cherry, nectarine, peach
 1. the paramedic is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 2. the person eating cherry is the paramedic##1
 3. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 4. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 5. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 6. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1
 7. the photographer is the person eating garlic##1
 8. the electrician is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 9. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
10. the person eating papaya is on the left of the mechanic##1
11. the videographer is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | photographer | paramedic | entrepreneur | mechanic | electrician | social-worker | videographer |
| Food   | garlic    | cherry   | papaya      | nectarine | apple    | strawberry    | peach         |

