.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, eggplant, nectarine, peach, raspberry, watermelon
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, ranch-style, victorian, modern, futuristic, colonial
 1. the modern house is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the colonial house##1
 3. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the victorian house##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the modern house is in the middle##1
 8. the modern house is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the colonial house is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cranberry | cucumber | peach | nectarine | raspberry | watermelon | eggplant |
| House   | farmhouse      | ranch-style   | victorian   | modern      | gothic-revival       | colonial       | futuristic     |

