.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
7 different games are played: bridge, snooker, billiard, go, domino, poker, chess
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, egyptian, indian, indonesian, nigerian, thai
 1. the person playing domino is the australian##1
 2. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 3. the nigerian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 5. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
 7. the egyptian is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the person playing billiard is the indonesian##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
11. the thai is the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Game   | poker    | chess     | go     | billiard      | snooker | domino      | bridge     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian | indonesian | thai | australian | argentine |

