 3. the british is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the nigerian##1
 5. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the polish##1
 8. the colombian is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the british##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Nationality   | dutch  | british | american | colombian | malaysian     | nigerian | polish |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller      | trike | motorbike    | skateboard | jet-ski   | boat  |

