.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-8::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, dancing, filmmaking, gardening, puzzles, rock-climbing, woodworking
7 different pets are kept: goat, snake, dog, lizard, ferret, goldfish, chinchilla
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is the owner of the dog##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby       | dancing   | gardening | woodworking | rock-climbing | baking     | filmmaking | puzzles |
| Pet   | dog | goldfish      | goat        | chinchilla         | snake | lizard     | ferret |

