.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-9::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, corn, grapes, kiwi, papaya, radish, watermelon
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, montecristo, baccarat, vegafina, dannemann, alhambra, bongani
 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the swisher-smoker is in the middle##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the dannemann-smoker is the person eating radish##1
 7. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 8. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating corn##1
10. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
11. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
| Food        | corn | broccoli | grapes | kiwi     | radish | watermelon | papaya |
| Cigar   | alhambra | vegafina  | bongani    | swisher | dannemann | montecristo       | baccarat   |

